                <p>Creating a suitable living environment is crucial for horse well-being:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Stabling:</strong> Provide a clean, dry stable with proper ventilation and space for movement.</li>
                    <li><strong>Pasture:</strong> Access to pasture for grazing and exercise is important for physical and mental health.</li>
                    <li><strong>Temperature:</strong> Protect horses from extreme weather with appropriate shelter and blankets if needed.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Ensure regular cleaning of stables and check for any hazards in the environment that could cause injury.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

