                <p>Preventing and managing common health issues in horses:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Colic:</strong> Monitor diet and exercise to prevent gastrointestinal problems.</li>
                    <li><strong>Laminitis:</strong> Avoid sudden changes in diet and ensure proper hoof care.</li>
                    <li><strong>Respiratory Issues:</strong> Maintain good ventilation and avoid exposure to dust or mold.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Regular veterinary check-ups and vaccinations are essential to maintaining health.</p>
            </div>
