                    <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Provide regular exercise to keep horses fit and healthy.</li>
                    <li><strong>Hoof Care:</strong> Regular farrier visits to trim and care for hooves are essential.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Establish a routine that includes daily care, regular check-ups, and preventive measures.</p>
